modName: Ravenhearst Style Backpack Stash All Buttons
modShortDescription: This mod adds Stash All, Stash Stacks and Stack Similar buttons to the backpack. It appears like the Ravenhearst formatted stash buttons.
modDescription:
This mod adds **Stash All**, **Stash Stacks** and **Stack Similar** buttons to the backpack. Modified from KhaineGB’s Mod so it appears like the [Ravenhearst](https://7daystodiemods.com/ravenhearst-mod/) formatted stash buttons.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/JaxTeller718/A19ModletsJax/tree/a19b168/JaxTeller718_BackpackStashAll)** for A19  
**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/JaxTeller718/JaxTeller718_Modlets_Stable/tree/master/JaxTeller718_BackpackStashAll)** for A18
